Demi Rose, 26, titillated fans as she shared a new snap from her holidays in the Caribbean. The model posed fully nude on a subbed as she soaked in the sunshine in St Lucia. The snap, shared with her 19 million Instagram followers, showed Demi laying face down on a sunbed. The social media personality wore nothing but an extra large straw hat. Demi looked away from the camera while the background revealed the picturesque mountains of St Lucia. She captioned the post: “I’ll send you a postcard.” Previous videos and pictures of the trip gave fans an insight into Demi’s lavish lifestyle, which includes swimming in an infinity pool while sipping a drink.